\begin_inset Formula $\int_{E}\lim_{t\rightarrow1}|f(x)-f(tx)|d\lambda<\frac{\varepsilon}{2}$
\end_inset

, and thus that 
\begin_inset Formula $\int_{\R}\lim_{t\rightarrow1}|f(x)-f(tx)|d\lambda<\frac{\varepsilon}{2}+\frac{\varepsilon}{2}=\varepsilon$
\end_inset

.
